Reversi Game
  author: hashiwa
  language: Java

Build:
  compile: JDK 8 or later
  $ mvn clean package

Run:
Available game modes (after building with 'mvn clean package'):

1. Player vs Computer:
  $ mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass="jp.hashiwa.reversi.play.PlayerVSComputer" -Dexec.args="[computer_player_class]"
    computer_player_class: 使用するコンピュータプレイヤークラス名（省略可）
  
2. Player vs Player:
  $ mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass="jp.hashiwa.reversi.play.PlayerVSPlayer"

3. Computer vs Computer:
  $ mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass="jp.hashiwa.reversi.play.ComputerVSComputer" -Dexec.args="[player1_class] [player2_class]"

Or build jar and run:
  $ mvn clean package
  $ java -cp target/reversi-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar jp.hashiwa.reversi.play.PlayerVSComputer

Available player classes:
- AlphaBetaPlayer (PlayerVSComputerのデフォルト)
- BiasedABPlayer 
- BiasedMMPlayer
- BiasedSimpleMMPlayer
- EdgePreferringPlayerType0
- EdgePreferringPlayerType1
- EdgePrefferingPlayer
- MinMaxPlayer
- RandomPlayer
- RationalPlayer
- SimpleMinMaxPlayer

System properties:
  jp.hashiwa.reversi.cellnum         : ゲームボードの縦横のセル数(int)
  jp.hashiwa.reversi.computerinterval: コンピュータが駒を打つまでの最低時間（秒）(int)
  jp.hashiwa.reversi.minmax.depth    : MinMax法で探索する深さ(int)
  jp.hashiwa.reversi.alphabeta.depth : AlphaBeta法で探索する深さ(int)
  jp.hashiwa.reversi.debug           : デバッグメッセージを出力(boolean)
